 the chopped up cucumber in a blender with the lemon and lime juice and ginger. Blend together, the mixture will be thick and can be filtered, serve as preferred. Ingredients Squeeze your orange juice and lemon juice, chop up the pineapple, and blend with the ginger . Sieve the pineapple juice together with the lemon juice. Ingredients Chop up the mangoes and put in a blender, add the already squeezed  lemon and orange juice and blend in the blender till smooth.  